  "title": "TiFlash returns different result from TiKV for LAST_VALUE window function with CROSS JOIN",
  "description": "## Bug Report\n\nPlease answer these questions before submitting your issue. Thanks!\n\n### 1. Minimal reproduce step (Required)\n```sql\nDROP TABLE IF EXISTS t0;\nDROP TABLE IF EXISTS t1;\nCREATE TABLE t0(id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY , c0 DATETIME);\nCREATE TABLE t1 LIKE t0;\nALTER TABLE t0 SET TIFLASH REPLICA 1;\nALTER TABLE t1 SET TIFLASH REPLICA 1;\nINSERT INTO t0(c0) VALUES ('4693-09-12 01:29:20');\nREPLACE INTO t1(c0) VALUES ('1051-03-01 01:50:39');\nINSERT INTO t1(c0) VALUES ('4257-08-10 19:07:42'), ('8539-02-01 14:30:43');\nINSERT IGNORE  INTO t0(c0) VALUES ('2896-09-04 00:12:05'), ('6040-07-31 13:04:25');\nREPLACE INTO t0(c0) VALUES ('6572-09-27 20:03:36');\nREPLACE INTO t0(c0) VALUES ('5393-06-13 12:48:02');\n\nSELECT /*+ read_from_storage(tikv[t0]) read_from_storage(tikv[t1]) */LAST_VALUE(t1.c0) OVER (ORDER BY t0.id) AS wf_0 FROM t1 CROSS JOIN  t0 WHERE t1.id > 1;\nSELECT /*+ read_from_storage(tiflash[t0]) read_from_storage(tiflash[t1]) */LAST_VALUE(t1.c0) OVER (ORDER BY t0.id) AS wf_0 FROM t1 CROSS JOIN  t0 WHERE t1.id > 1;\n\n```\n<!-- a step by step guide for reproducing the bug. -->\n\n### 2. What did you expect to see? (Required)\nThe same query returns the same results on both TiKV and TiFlash.\n### 3. What did you see instead (Required)\n```sql\nmysql> SELECT /*+ read_from_storage(tikv[t0]) read_from_storage(tikv[t1]) */LAST_VALUE(t1.c0) OVER (ORDER BY t0.id) AS wf_0 FROM t1 CROSS JOIN  t0 WHERE t1.id > 1;\n+---------------------+\n| wf_0                |\n+---------------------+\n| 4257-08-10 19:07:42 |\n| 4257-08-10 19:07:42 |\n| 4257-08-10 19:07:42 |\n| 4257-08-10 19:07:42 |\n| 4257-08-10 19:07:42 |\n| 4257-08-10 19:07:42 |\n| 4257-08-10 19:07:42 |\n| 4257-08-10 19:07:42 |\n| 4257-08-10 19:07:42 |\n| 4257-08-10 19:07:42 |\n+---------------------+\n10 rows in set (0.00 sec)\n\nmysql> SELECT /*+ read_from_storage(tiflash[t0]) read_from_storage(tiflash[t1]) */LAST_VALUE(t1.c0) OVER (ORDER BY t0.id) AS wf_0 FROM t1 CROSS JOIN  t0 WHERE t1.id > 1;\n+---------------------+\n| wf_0                |\n+---------------------+\n| 8539-02-01 14:30:43 |\n| 8539-02-01 14:30:43 |\n| 8539-02-01 14:30:43 |\n| 8539-02-01 14:30:43 |\n| 8539-02-01 14:30:43 |\n| 8539-02-01 14:30:43 |\n| 8539-02-01 14:30:43 |\n| 8539-02-01 14:30:43 |\n| 8539-02-01 14:30:43 |\n| 8539-02-01 14:30:43 |\n+---------------------+\n10 rows in set (0.02 sec)\n```\n### 4. What is your TiDB version? (Required)\n```\n+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+\n| tidb_version()                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |\n+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+\n| Release Version: v9.0.0-beta.1.pre-918-g4419a28\nEdition: Community\nGit Commit Hash: 4419a28eb9cd988a7f2959c400aa21a63ee884fa\nGit Branch: HEAD\nUTC Build Time: 2025-06-11 05:47:23\nGoVersion: go1.23.10\nRace Enabled: false\nCheck Table Before Drop: false\nStore: tikv\nKernel Type: Classic |\n+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+\n```\n<!-- Paste the output of SELECT tidb_version() -->\n\n",
